========================================
README for CALLA 1.3
========================================
- unzip the archive to any directory
- start the demo by CALLA.sh or CALLA.exe

========================
Changes in v1.3
========================
- Product rebrand from SYMPLiK to symboltree.com
- Use log4j for logging. Logging parameters removed.
  * add log4j-api-2.6.2.jar, log4j-core-2.6.2.jar in classpath; log4j2.xml in current dir.
- change button text to icons
- add help button and parameter "flower.help.file"

========================
Changes in v1.2
========================
- Add Choice pagination features controlled by flower.choice.size and flower.choice.max parameters
- Add Exit confirmation, controlled by parameter "flower.exit.comfirm"
- Add splash screen hook in GUI mode

========================
Changes in v1.1
========================
- Use JDOM 2
- Java 7 compatible

========================
Changes in v1.0 build 73
========================
- Add text-based directory and file browser
- Fix line wrap logic in GUI mode; allow to line wrap text by using Question.lineWrap() method
- Put "[B] Back" and "[X] Exit" on the same line
- Add new example for tutorial (set flower.start=symplik.flower.sample.TestIntroduction to see it)

========================
Changes in v1.0 build 52
========================
- Initial release